CHRISTMAS WINNING NOTIFICATION

Your e- mail address attached to ticket number: 275-189-657-23-05 with Serial number 8756-05 drew the lucky numbers and bonus ball number which subsequently won you the lottery in the 2nd category.You have therefore been approved to claim a total sum  (EIGHT HUNDRED THOUSAND U.S DOLLARS) in cash credit file ref:ILP/HW 47509/02.
